WEBVTT

06:05.149 --> 06:08.451
<i>the most beautiful was</i>
<i>a public pool in Paris.</i>

06:08.453 --> 06:10.386
<i>That the water</i>
<i>there was so clear,</i>

06:10.388 --> 06:12.555
<i>you could make</i>
<i>your morning cofe</i>
<i>with it.</i>

06:12.557 --> 06:15.558
<i>That a single swim</i>
<i>there changed his life.</i>
